source 'http://github.com/joejulian/joejulian-packages'
author 'joejulian'
license 'Apache License, Version 2.0'
summary 'Classes to install packages common to multiple other classes'
description 'Since multiple classes often require the same packages, conflicts occur. This module abstracts the dependencies within classes to allow them to be included multiple times.'
project_page 'http://github.com/joejulian/joejulian-packages'

## dependencies:
dependency 'joejulian/yum'
